## Layout (the numbered spine)
```
{{DIR00}}/   charter, scope baseline + ledger, roles
01-intake/       raw inputs (transcripts, notes, reference, from-brain)
02-deliverables/ sprint-scoped team outputs
03-status/       decision log, hours, tasks
{{DIR04}}/ {{DIR04_DESC}}
05-personal/     per-member private workspace
```

## Working here
- Log decisions in `03-status/decision-log.md` (see `.claude/rules/decision-log.md`).
- Log hours in your `05-personal/<name>/03-status/hours-log.md`.
- Promote work via the flow in `.claude/rules/publishing.md`.
- Run the harnesses in `.claude/skills/` (decision-audit, scope-creep, weekly-synthesis).
- Validate structure with the Agentic Team Ops validators.

## Team Brain (optional)
This repo can sync tier-tagged content to an AIOS Team Brain. Configure
`aios.yaml` + `.env` (see `.env.example`), then:
```
aios status   # what would sync (and what's blocked, and why)
aios push     # push team/external-tier content
aios pull     # fetch team updates into 01-intake/from-brain/
aios query "what did we decide about X?"
```
`access: admin` content and untagged files never leave this machine.
